5
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:38,520
[Land of Dreams]

6
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:41,340
[Episode 10]

7
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:04,140
Brother,

8
00:01:04,420 --> 00:01:05,820
am I the closest person to you?

9
00:01:06,220 --> 00:01:06,900
Brother,

10
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:09,620
I'm obedient.

11
00:01:18,420 --> 00:01:20,300
Ye Xiaosheng, what are you up to?

12
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:22,300
A sister,

13
00:01:23,020 --> 00:01:24,100
a disciple,

14
00:01:25,140 --> 00:01:26,260
what's on your mind?

15
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:38,460
Mengchen.

16
00:01:39,300 --> 00:01:40,740
Why didn't you knock on the door?

17
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:45,100
What's wrong with your shoulder?

18
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:45,820
Did you get hurt?

19
00:01:45,820 --> 00:01:46,420
No.

20
00:01:46,900 --> 00:01:48,620
How could I possibly get hurt?

21
00:01:51,180 --> 00:01:52,420
Are you keeping something from me?

22
00:01:52,940 --> 00:01:53,860
If you're not hurt,

23
00:01:54,020 --> 00:01:55,060
why don't you let me check?

24
00:01:56,860 --> 00:01:58,420
You're acting strange.

25
00:01:58,420 --> 00:01:59,860
Why are you insisting
on pulling at my clothes?

26
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:01,060
I don't want to be kept in the dark.

27
00:02:25,060 --> 00:02:26,220
Mengchen! Mengchen!

28
00:02:27,820 --> 00:02:28,620
Mengchen.

29
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:37,740
What am I doing?

30
00:02:38,580 --> 00:02:40,540
Even if I think Mengchen resembles Guyu,

31
00:02:40,940 --> 00:02:42,340
I shouldn't verify it like this.

32
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:13,980
M...Mengchen.

33
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:16,140
Why did you pack your bags?

34
00:03:16,140 --> 00:03:17,340
I'm heading to Zeyu's clinic.

35
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:18,140
That's not okay.

36
00:03:18,660 --> 00:03:19,580
He's a man.

37
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:20,980
Aren't you also a man?

38
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:23,020
Mengchen,

39
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:27,180
I was wrong. I shouldn't have done that.

40
00:03:27,460 --> 00:03:29,380
But staying overnight at a man's place

41
00:03:29,380 --> 00:03:30,500
is dangerous.

42
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:31,500
Brother,

43
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:33,660
you kissed me
and tried to take my clothes off.

44
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:35,380
Who's the real danger here?

45
00:03:39,540 --> 00:03:41,380
I'm sorry.

46
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:43,340
But I was worried

47
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:46,220
that you might keep something from me.

48
00:03:46,220 --> 00:03:47,580
What have I kept from you?

49
00:03:48,740 --> 00:03:49,540
Brother,

50
00:03:49,940 --> 00:03:50,940
let me ask you.

51
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:55,500
Do you have any secrets from me?

52
00:03:56,020 --> 00:03:58,340
Have you ever kept anything from me?

53
00:04:07,660 --> 00:04:08,460
Mengchen.

54
00:04:09,980 --> 00:04:10,780
Mengchen.

55
00:04:10,780 --> 00:04:15,120
♪A glance seals our fate♪

56
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:20,860
♪Without you, time fades into night♪

57
00:04:20,860 --> 00:04:21,660
Nice!

58
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:23,180
You truly are a heroine.

59
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:33,220
When you came to the clinic yesterday,

60
00:04:33,420 --> 00:04:34,300
I wanted to ask

61
00:04:35,180 --> 00:04:36,980
if you had a fight with Xiaosheng.

62
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:41,220
My brother was suspicious of my injury.

63
00:04:41,780 --> 00:04:44,300
Thank goodness you helped me cover it
with a mold in advance.

64
00:04:45,020 --> 00:04:48,060
Otherwise, my cover
would have been blown.

65
00:04:49,820 --> 00:04:50,620
But Mengchen,

66
00:04:51,380 --> 00:04:53,060
why must you keep everything

67
00:04:53,140 --> 00:04:54,740
a secret from Xiaosheng?

68
00:04:56,420 --> 00:04:57,460
He's your family.

69
00:04:57,620 --> 00:04:58,900
He wouldn't hurt you, right?

70
00:05:01,460 --> 00:05:03,900
I have my reasons for keeping secrets.

71
00:05:05,140 --> 00:05:05,940
For family,

72
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:08,340
I would protect with my life.

73
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:10,380
But for an enemy...

74
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:01,540
Master, what's going on?

75
00:06:03,620 --> 00:06:05,020
Why did you approach the secret chamber?

76
00:06:06,540 --> 00:06:07,500
Secret chamber?

77
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:09,340
What secret chamber?

78
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:11,460
Shaozi knocked you out

79
00:06:11,940 --> 00:06:13,540
for tampering with the chamber's lock.

80
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:16,100
All assassins
who join the Blood Sacrifice Gang

81
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:17,260
are bound by a rule.

82
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:20,060
Without permission,
no one can approach the secret chamber.

83
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:22,300
It's a taboo.

84
00:06:22,940 --> 00:06:24,340
I know, Master.

85
00:06:25,020 --> 00:06:26,940
I just lost my way.

86
00:06:26,940 --> 00:06:28,460
It wasn't intentional.

87
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:29,500
Lost your way?

88
00:06:30,340 --> 00:06:33,100
Is there another explanation
you'd like to offer?

89
00:06:33,780 --> 00:06:35,060
Coach, the medicine is ready.

90
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:47,500
This is the Heart-burning Powder,

91
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:50,340
specifically designed to test loyalty.

92
00:06:51,260 --> 00:06:52,820
An hour after ingestion,

93
00:06:52,820 --> 00:06:55,580
you'll feel as if countless ants
are eating your heart out.

94
00:06:55,580 --> 00:06:57,420
It'll compel you to confess everything.

95
00:06:58,620 --> 00:07:00,100
Since you've approached
the secret chamber,

96
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:02,420
you owe the Gang an explanation.

97
00:07:02,860 --> 00:07:06,140
You are under my lead

98
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:07,340
and served as my disciple.

99
00:07:08,140 --> 00:07:09,580
I'd spare you the torture

100
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:11,140
of the Heart-burning Powder if possible.

101
00:07:12,940 --> 00:07:13,940
I've told you everything

102
00:07:14,540 --> 00:07:16,020
there is to tell.

103
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:18,060
Now, think it over.

104
00:07:22,700 --> 00:07:25,020
Master, I didn't.

105
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:28,020
I was just scouting the routes
as you ordered.

106
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:29,900
It was an accident
that I ended up there.

107
00:07:30,860 --> 00:07:32,740
Coach, don't bother interrogating her.

108
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:34,060
Drinking this,

109
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:36,180
she'll confess everything.

110
00:07:36,820 --> 00:07:38,580
Forget it. Boss is waiting.

111
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:50,500
Physician Ge,

112
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:54,700
Guyu is my personally trained disciple.

113
00:07:54,900 --> 00:07:57,100
If she's a spy, we can't let her off.

114
00:07:57,220 --> 00:07:58,420
But we can't wrong her either.

115
00:07:58,980 --> 00:07:59,980
Keep an eye on her.

116
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:02,820
I'll go check the route
she took back today.

117
00:08:10,370 --> 00:08:11,100
[Nanyan Residence]

118
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:11,900
Mengchen!

119
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:12,980
Mengchen!

120
00:08:13,660 --> 00:08:14,460
Mengchen!

121
00:08:15,660 --> 00:08:16,460
Mengchen!

122
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:24,020
[Huaicheng Art School]

123
00:08:32,020 --> 00:08:32,820
Qi Zeyu!

124
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:36,540
Bro, what's up?

125
00:08:36,740 --> 00:08:37,980
Tell me where Mengchen is.

126
00:08:38,140 --> 00:08:39,580
How much is she keeping from me?

127
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:42,780
This is a matter of life and death.

128
00:08:42,780 --> 00:08:43,780
Where exactly is she?

129
00:08:44,540 --> 00:08:46,220
I really don't know.

130
00:08:57,020 --> 00:08:57,820
Go.

131
00:08:58,060 --> 00:08:58,900
Hurry!

132
00:08:59,220 --> 00:09:00,020
Master!

133
00:09:00,380 --> 00:09:01,180
Master!

134
00:09:01,900 --> 00:09:02,700
Master!

135
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:03,860
Don't move!

136
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:04,900
Master!

137
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:06,460
Master!

138
00:09:07,700 --> 00:09:08,500
Master!

139
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:14,860
Master.

140
00:09:15,140 --> 00:09:15,940
Master.

141
00:09:19,780 --> 00:09:20,580
Boss,

142
00:09:20,820 --> 00:09:23,660
I'm the one at fault.
Let the punishment be on me!

143
00:09:28,380 --> 00:09:29,980
Your master
didn't discipline you properly.

144
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:31,540
Qingming,

145
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:33,220
you've been negligent.

146
00:09:33,580 --> 00:09:34,980
How could you forget

147
00:09:35,340 --> 00:09:38,020
that the secret chamber is off-limits?

148
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:41,540
That's a violation
of the most crucial rule of the Gang.

149
00:09:43,060 --> 00:09:43,900
Boss,

150
00:09:44,260 --> 00:09:45,060
I accept the punishment.

151
00:09:46,140 --> 00:09:46,980
I accept it.

152
00:09:48,260 --> 00:09:49,820
It was my fault.

153
00:09:51,020 --> 00:09:52,100
Please spare Guyu.

154
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:54,020
No, Master.

155
00:09:54,940 --> 00:09:56,340
It was my fault.

156
00:09:57,060 --> 00:09:58,700
Just punish me, please!

157
00:09:59,060 --> 00:10:02,260
It's good that a master and disciple
can support each other.

158
00:10:02,820 --> 00:10:03,620
Guyu,

159
00:10:04,060 --> 00:10:05,300
take your master for treatment.

160
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:23,300
I'll get Physician Ge
to tend to your injuries.

161
00:10:27,220 --> 00:10:28,780
Did you get hurt just now?

162
00:10:31,420 --> 00:10:33,180
Don't ever do anything so foolish again.

163
00:10:34,940 --> 00:10:38,140
I'm fine, Master.
Your injuries are more serious.

164
00:10:40,020 --> 00:10:40,820
Tell me

165
00:10:42,100 --> 00:10:43,340
why you joined the Blood Sacrifice Gang.

166
00:10:46,580 --> 00:10:48,100
If you don't tell me the truth,

167
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:49,980
I'll have you
take the Heart-burning Powder.

168
00:10:54,420 --> 00:10:55,740
You still don't trust me?

169
00:10:59,340 --> 00:11:00,140
Fine.

170
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:04,140
I'll take the Heart-burning Powder myself.

171
00:11:23,260 --> 00:11:24,420
Stop the suspicions.

172
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:44,340
I am Guyu,

173
00:11:45,940 --> 00:11:46,740
someone

174
00:11:47,420 --> 00:11:49,220
who can stand by your side.

175
00:11:49,220 --> 00:11:51,080
♪Fate entwined♪

176
